            </source>
            <subjectClass>인사-임면(任免)</subjectClass>
          </biblioData>
        </front>
        <text>
          <content>
            <paragraph align="center">○壬辰/右議政<index num="1563820_0" ref="M_0004548" sort="K" type="이름">李世白</index>呈病, 乞針灸暇。</paragraph>
            <paragraph align="center">
              <postScript type="史論">
                <paragraph align="center">【史臣曰: "<index num="1563821_0" ref="M_0004548" sort="K" type="이름">世白</index>沈凝寡言笑, 處事多果毅, 律身頗淸儉, 但在銓地, 專事黨論, 用舍甚偏, 及爲相, 以沮遏言路, 斥逐異己, 爲事業, 使近來士論益乖激, 皆世白之罪也。"】</paragraph>
              </postScript>
            </paragraph>
          </content>
        </text>
      </level5>
